<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact - My Airbnb Collaborations</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('images/background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
        }
        .text-link {
            display: block;
            margin: 10px;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
        .profile {
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .profile img {
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile">
        <img src="images/your_photo.jpg" alt="Your Photo">
        <p>Hello! I'm Federico Di Summa. Ever since I was young, I've always wanted to travel the world. I found a way to turn this passion into my profession by collaborating with Airbnb hosts around the globe.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <img src="icons/whatsapp.png" alt="WhatsApp" class="icon">
        <a href="https://wa.me/393286878645" class="text-link">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <img src="icons/instagram.png" alt="Instagram" class="icon">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/federicodisumma/" class="text-link">Instagram</a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <img src="icons/email.png" alt="Email" class="icon">
        <a href="mailto:disummafederico@gmail.com" class="text-link">Email</a>
    </div>
    <script>
        let currentBackground = 1;
        setInterval(() => {
            currentBackground = currentBackground === 1 ? 2 : 1;
            document.body.style.backgroundImage = `url('images/background_${currentBackground}.jpg')`;
        }, 30000); // 30000 milliseconds = 30 seconds
    </script>
</body>
</html>
